data.description: Stunning & Meticulous custom built home in the iconic neighborhood of Southall Landing Marina Community! Southall Landing includes access to tennis courts, 2 pools, basketball court, clubhouse & workout facility overlooking the marina, racquetball, boat slips can be rented. You are greeted with a grand double foyer entry/w additional loft space above (use for an office space/flex space)! This home features a front porch, an expansive back deck (with hot tub hook ups) & a outdoor chef station, new tiled kitchen floors with granite, high ceilings including 2 living spaces (main living room is 2 story) w/ gas fireplace. FIRST FLOOR PRIMARY BEDROOM ENSUITE leading directly to a private deck with a wooded lot view. Expansive lot with loads of parking options, including 3 additional spaces behind the home!Your new home has quick access to the clubhouse and marina and located just yards away. Enjoy your new home near the Marina/Buckroe Beach/I64/664/The Shipyard and Langley Airforce base!
